oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thompson Hall terrace
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of a man standing on a terrace in a field in the Thompson Hall community. The earthwork was constructed under the supervision of the Extension Service. The man is holding land surveying instruments.
